summary: Swiss - Chilean professional with more than 10 years of experience, having the opportunity to develop my career in two different countries. Involved in the review and improvement of processes, working transversally at all levels of the companies. Currently I am in the end of a one-year trip around the world, collecting several life experiences that have helped me to be more conscious about different realities, as well as being a more adaptable, open-minded and flexible person.
